@startuml
skinparam backgroundColor white
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam sequence {
  ArrowColor Black
  LifeLineBorderColor Black
  LifeLineBackgroundColor White
  ParticipantBorderColor Black
  ParticipantBackgroundColor White
  ActorBorderColor Black
  ActorBackgroundColor White
  ParticipantFontColor Black
  ActorFontColor Black
}

actor "User" as User
participant "Frontend" as UI
participant "Backend API\nPOST /api/invoices/:id/pay" as API
participant "Database\nTable: Wallet" as WalletDB
participant "Database\nTable: WalletTx" as WalletTxDB
participant "Database\nTable: Transaction" as TxDB
participant "Database\nTable: Invoice" as InvoiceDB
participant "Database\nTable: Receipt" as ReceiptDB
participant "Ethereum/Hardhat" as Chain
User->UI: Confirm invoice payment
UI->API: Submit invoice payment request
API->WalletDB: Validate wallet balance and deduct payment amount
WalletDB-->API: Wallet updated
API->WalletTxDB: Store wallet payment movement
WalletTxDB-->API: Wallet transaction stored
API->TxDB: Store invoice payment transaction
TxDB-->API: Payment transaction stored
API->InvoiceDB: Update invoice status to paid
InvoiceDB-->API: Invoice updated
API->ReceiptDB: Create or retrieve receipt
ReceiptDB-->API: Receipt ready
API->Chain: Publish payment verification proof
Chain-->API: Return txHash and block metadata
API->TxDB: Update verification status
TxDB-->API: Verification updated
API-->UI: Return payment result
UI-->User: Display payment result and transaction status

@enduml
